        <h3>Instructions</h3>
        <div class="help-content">
          <ol>
            <li>Format your document so that each question begins with a number followed by a period (e.g., ‚Äú1.‚Äù) and options are lettered.</li>
            <li>Include an ‚ÄúAnswer Key‚Äù section at the end with answers for each question.</li>
            <li>Select the export format.</li>
            <li>Click "Convert Document".</li>
            <li>When conversion is complete, click "Download Quiz File".</li>
            <li>Import the file into your LMS.</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>
